WEBVTT

00:00.427 --> 00:01.184
Excuse me.

00:01.414 --> 00:03.112
Is there a news agency near here?

00:03.411 --> 00:05.438
Yes. There is one in Berry Street.

00:05.582 --> 00:06.289
Where is that?

00:06.673 --> 00:10.167
Go along this road and turn right. That's Berry Street.

00:10.578 --> 00:15.049
Go past the pub and the news agency is on the right, opposite the supermarket.

00:15.489 --> 00:18.699
So, I go along this road and turn right...

00:19.217 --> 00:21.480
...then I go past the pub and...

00:21.829 --> 00:23.719
And the news agency is on the right.

00:24.045 --> 00:25.307
Opposite the supermarket.

00:25.475 --> 00:26.883
Oh, great! Thanks a lot.

00:26.990 --> 00:27.552
No problem.

